<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-15021] KRaft controller increases leader epoch when shrinking ISR</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-15021</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the KRaft controller shrinks the ISR it also forces the leader epoch to increase. This is unnecessary and cases all of the follower replica fetches to get invalidated.&lt;/p&gt;

